text: Blaichach is a municipality in the district of Oberallgäu in Bavaria in Germany. It is in the northeast of the municipality the Iller flows through Blaichach. Blaichach was first mentioned as Bilaicha in 1275. Between 1988 and 2008 Blaichach grew by 599 people. == References == Category:Oberallgäu
